三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程為共同選修課程。學生在修習本課程之後，能熟悉閱讀策略，並將所學應用於日常的閱讀以及學科領域的閱讀之中；對於師培生而言，更能將此經驗在日後的教學生涯中，幫助學生成為一個成功的讀者和學習者。 


This course is a common selective course. After finishing the course, students become familiar with various kind of reading strategies and skills, which can be applied to reading in daily reading materials as well as professional's. For those teachers-to-be, they are able to apply what they learn from this course to their future teaching career, and help students become successful readers and learners. 


