二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsListening Pro 3, Total Mastery of TOEIC Listening Skills
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online ResourcesTEDGEPTEZtest


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程加強學生之聽力訓練及基本語言測驗技巧 


This course introduces listening strategies to help students familiarize themselves with a variety of spoken discourses, such as English-conducted classes,social interactions, and business meetings. Preparation for standardized tests is also emphasized. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionThis course is developed to help intermediate to upper intermediate learners improve their English communication and listening ability. Quizzes will be given regularly in class and online exercises will be assigned.

